					   <td>

			
			
			


<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">
<tr>
	<td width="1%">&nbsp;</td>
	<td width="98%">
	
		<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">
		<tr>

		
			<tr>
				<td><font face="verdana" size="1">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="/quests/default.asp">Quests</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="default.asp?land=121215">East Cabilis</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline3.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<b>Shestar's Scaled Coif</b><br><br>
				</td>
			</tr>
				
			<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    Shestar's Scaled Coif</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=161020"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><a href="mailto:aragond1@aol.com">Kommodoe</a> | 
		                        6/23/2000 5:05:28 PM</b></font></p>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">OK here is this quest. It's very easy and the coif looks really cool.<BR>
<BR>
1) hail Trooper Shestar. he is located on the path on the right into East Cabilis from the Field of Bone.<BR>
<BR>
2) give him 3 loose scales (pink, stackable ones) and 5 gp.<BR>
<BR>
3) he gives you a Shestar's Unfinished Coif. don't despair, you'll still get it. take that to the forge and also put in another 3 loose scales(don't stack the scales, put them in seperately).<BR>
<BR>
4)there is no fourth step.<BR>
<BR>
This item requires some blacksmithing skill, but i haven't failed yet at skill level 23.<BR>
It is as follows:<BR>
Shestar's Scaled Coif<BR>
ac:4<BR>
LORE ITEM<BR>
pretty much every iksar class can equip it(even monks)<BR>
<BR>
it looks really cool on your character mod too.well, that's it.<BR>
if you keep failing, tell me and i'll make ya one. ;&gt;<BR>
<BR>
Kommodoe<BR>
Iksar Shaman of the 7th level<BR>
Bristlebane Server
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
					</p>
			</td>
			</tr>
